description_en:
- Cleaning the face to prepare for moisturizing or nourishing;
- Exfoliating dead skin to reveal a radiant, youthful skin;
- Timely supply of water and nutrition to the skin to prevent aging;
- Removing hard cells under foot or elbow;
- Reduces rough and callus skin;
- Increases and improves circulation;
- Discover the spa experience of hand and foot;
- Microdermabrasion at home to gently exfoliate, polish, and smooth rough, callus skin;
- Rotating hand-held resurfacing tool exfoliates dull surface-layers to improve skin texture, and increases micro-circulation.
How yo Use :
- Daily step 1: For daily cleansing, use the Normal or the Extra Sensitive brush depending on your skin type.
- Daily step 2: Once your skin is clean and dry, use the Beauty Sponge to evenly apply moisturizing cream or serum. You can also use the sponge to apply the foundation.
- Weekly: We recommend using the Exfoliation brush once a week to remove dry skin and enhance your natural glow.
- Quarterly: To maintain your beauty set, always rinse the brushes after use. For maximum performance and hygiene, we recommend replacing the brushes every 3 months.
